phrases: Far beyond the deep blue Earth, you and I shall meet...
A snow-white feather will come fluttering down, swaying gently in the air.
Without holding back, I want to envelope you, my one and only love.
I know I have the power to protect the one I love, right here in my hands.
Just as I have always dreamed.
Let the wind carry off your hopes, faraway.
I have wings nobody can see.
They will take us to where we can be free.
This is a one-in-a-million chance, so you have got to do your best.
If nothing comes of this, I will toss a thunderbolt at you!
I will not have it, I tell you!
You lay one finger on my Big Sister and...
Do not listen to her, she is a child.
Do not listen to a wicked old hag like her!
Give it a read, and you will know exactly what to do.
Do you even understand what it is about?
Since Skuld and I have to go back to Heaven for about a week...
Really...these sisters are totally in sync, huh?
If You are a Real Man, Save the Goddess?
Let us hang you in the sunshine... let us hang you in the sunshine...
Just because we are alone together does not mean anything's going to change...
I mean, Belldandy is not the type of girl to get all self-conscious.
This thing and that thing only happened because of the potion.
A whole week alone with her... what are we supposed to do?
Actually, I mean...what should I do?
I guess I should not worry about it.
Is this ever going to end?
Not if you do not stop goofing off, it will not.
I wonder if everything's going well with Keiichi?
I would not bet on things going the way you want, Urd!
Because I fixed it so he will not be able to get near Big Sister!
How do you like Skuld's flan?
But I never would have thought Skuld would be into making desserts!
She really wanted you to have it.
She insisted I serve it to you.
Hey, I am not going to do anything.
Do not tell me I have turned into a girl?
You will remain a member of that gender until I return.
That is what it says on this plate.
So that is why she made me eat her flan...
But from what I can see, it does not seem to be doing any physical harm.
I think if you just stay that way, it will wear off in about a week.
You mean I have to go to class like this?
Um...would you like to come with me to the ladies' room?
But are you sure you do not mind me coming along?
That is right, so it would not be strange at all, would it?
Why do not we all go to the public bath tonight?
Are you sure it is okay for me to come along?
We are all girls here, are not we?
But of course, you are right!
You have got to be kidding me.
You have got to be kidding me.
Is not there any way you can change me back right now?
Would you please lift up your shirt?
If I rub it all over your chest area, I think you will go back to normal.
You are not going to do the rubbing, are you?
I think an oral medication would be better.
I know, I can just mix it up with...
We are going to pour in that liquid and this seed at the same time.
Now then, I want you to pour it in gently.
There was a virus in that liquid.
As an additive, it can have an extremely potent effect, but if a goddess...
I should not have been so careless.
Let us get you to a doctor right away.
No, the doctors here on Earth would not know how to deal with a virus from Heaven.
I did not inhale all that much.
So if I just get some sleep tonight, I should make a quick recovery.
But there is still the matter of your body, Keiichi...
Hey, do not worry about it.
Since I am like this, maybe I will try putting some makeup on.
It might be very becoming on you!
We came over to hang out with you!
But she told me we should come over, because he would definitely be at home.
I am a distant cousin of Belldandy's, and...
Good thing I still had this costume from that farewell bash.
Oh, and thank you for coming over, but I am sorry to have to tell you...
He invites us over and then goes out?
Are Belldandy and the others around?
Well, Skuld and Urd are away on a trip, and...
Then it is fine by me.
The thing is, Belldandy is still asleep, and...
Oh, so you are all here.
And you really did try on some makeup!
So will not you please come in, everyone?
I do still have a little cough...
Belldandy's a babe, but that little Keiko gal...
She is got a great figure too.
It makes me feel so inadequate just seeing them stand there side by side.
I know I have seen her somewhere...
I am going to go make some tea, all right?
Oh boy...now what do I do?
Belldandy's not her usual self, do not you think?
Now that you mention it, she seemed a little unsteady on her feet.
She is been sick since last night?
We would better call for an ambulance.
We would better call for an ambulance.
Belldandy said she did not want to make a big deal out of this...
Uh, because we do not have any money!
If you pool all our money, there should be enough for Belldandy to see a doctor.
But if anyone's going to take care of Belldandy, I am the guy.
It makes me feel good to know how much you care.
Hasegawa, when is your next mechanical test again?
Actually, I cannot say until I know when the repairs will be done.
I ordered the parts the day before yesterday, so you can get started...
Anyway, tell Belldandy we all said to get well soon, okay?
Do you really think we should...
Well, Keiko's being so adamant about it.
We can leave it to her.
Kei-chan, I am pretty sure this whole drag thing has something to do with...
I mean, because now you can do something for Belldandy!
Damn, which one of these is real medicine?
Maybe if I go into Skuld's room I will find a machine that will clue me in.
It is been a whole night, but she is nowhere near better yet...
The medicine we have on Earth would not work on a goddess.
No matter how hard I try, I cannot do anything for her...
Belldandy never shows how she might be suffering inside...
I do not have any choice but to talk to Urd and Skuld directly in Heaven.
It might have been an accident, but my call did go through once.
I should have a chance, at least!
Hello, you have reached the Tokyo Broadcasting System.
I am not going to give up!
This is the Goddess Eye Clinic.
This is the Goddess Eye Clinic.
Thanks, but we are not interested.
I cannot do anything for you.
Deep down, I was sure it would somehow work out.
That if I really cared...that as long as I had faith...it would work out...
That as long as I had feelings for you, you would stay by my side forever...
Because it all begins with the heart...
Because it all begins when you believe...
Right now, I feel so at peace with myself.
Because I know how much you care, Keiichi...
Because I know in your heart you believe!
Right now, I feel so at peace with myself.
Because I know how much you care, Keiichi...
Because I know in your heart you believe!
If I am going to believe, then I have to believe in any miracle or coincidence.
My call is going to go through no matter what.
Belldandy will recover, no matter what!
Hello, you have reached the Goddess Help Line.
It is Belldandy...she is in trouble!
I do not know how you got through to us here.
It sounds like she is definitely taking a turn for the worse.
Unless we do something now, her body will be destroyed.
Listen carefully to what I am about to say.
We are going to need some wind crystals to concoct medicine for her.
So I should have those ready for you by the time you get back, right?
Who was that on the phone?
I am going back to Earth.
But wait, you are not done with your work yet, are you?
If you walk off the job, you will be severely punished!
I am doing it for my sister, and besides...
Wait, do not tell me that was Keiichi on the phone?
What is happened to Big Sister?
I am going to save you right now.
Take that to the highest place you can and hold it up to a fresh breeze.
That way, you will be able to catch the crystals.
I love being up in high places.
Because it looks like everyone in the world is groveling at my feet!
Okay, this is a good spot...
What do you think you are doing?
You cannot come up here, it is off-limits!
What are you going to use that for?
Come over here, it is dangerous!
This is the highest spot around here, is not it?
There is another level up there!
Do you have the wind crystals?
Yeah, I have got them, but...
Hey, what is a kid like you doing here?
Keiichi, you have got to jump!
If you do not hurry up, you will not be able to save Big Sister!
You have got to trust me!
We will have to give it to her mouth-to-mouth...
To tell you the truth, I was surprised.
You are the only one who is ever been able to call Heaven and make the connection.
I can see you really do care about Belldandy.
You cannot let him do that!
Just this one time, got that?
How dare you put your mouth against Big Sister's lips!
Oh well, since it made Big Sister better, I guess I will let it go.
Wait a minute... are not those bigger than mine?
These are at least 10 times as big as somebody is!
Just look at how red your face is!
You want me to make them bigger for you?
If I leave it to you, I will get a set of vulgar, sagging breasts like yours!
If you are jealous, then be honest and admit you are jealous!
Always believe in yourself and your Dreams.
I love you so much it hurts...
And it hurts me that I cannot tell you how I feel.
You and I have matching hearts...
So we must share the same scars deep down inside.
But now that I am in your arms, I think I can catch...
All we have to do is gaze at each other.
It is all right for your heart to flutter...
All we have to do is love each other.
Open your heart, and ride that favorable wind.
Do not run away from happiness.
I will always be waiting for you.
So come rest your wings anytime.
It is all right to cry... anytime you need to.
I just want to see you again...
All we have to do is love each other.
Open your heart, and ride that favorable wind.
I just want you to be happy.
Angels are the reflections of a goddess's soul...her other self.
The struggles of Urd's little sister remind her of her younger self.
What Would not I Give for an Angel With White Wings?!
In other words, hard work is the key for goddesses and humans.
